Date: Tue, 21 Jul 2026 15:02:27 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 15/17] Add POST /summary: generate end-of-session ticket text
 via Ollama

Calls the local gemma4:e4b model through Ollama's OpenAI-compatible API
using the artworks/testimonies the frontend already has client-side, then
stores the result in summaries.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 5 <noreply@anthropic.com>
